<bibRefCitation id="EF864B4BFFDAFF92FDC9F8DEFC94F84B" author="Krapp-Schickel, T." box="[590,842,1901,1926]" pageId="22" pageNumber="173" pagination="773 - 809" refId="ref21001" refString="Krapp-Schickel, T. (1993) Suborder Caprellidea. In: Ruffo, S. (Ed.), The Amphipoda. of the Mediterranean. Memoires de l'Institut oceanographique de Monaco, 13, 773 - 809." type="journal article" year="1993">Krapp-Schickel, 1993</bibRefCitation>
