<bibRefCitation id="EF864B4BFFDAFF92FEF4F822FCC0F867" author="Laubitz, D. R. &amp; Sorbe, J. C." box="[371,798,1937,1962]" pageId="22" pageNumber="173" pagination="626 - 632" refId="ref21383" refString="Laubitz, D. R. &amp; Sorbe, J. C. (1996) Deep-water caprellids (Amphipoda: Caprellidea) from the Bay of Biscay: a new species and a new locality record. Journal of Crustacean Biology, 16, 626 - 632. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 1548754" type="journal article" year="1996">Laubitz &amp; Sorbe, 1996; present study</bibRefCitation>
